== 頒發學位 ==
=== 本科教育<ref>{{cite web |author1=The University of Edinburgh |title=The University of Edinburgh |url=https://www.ed.ac.uk/divinity/undergraduate |website=Undergraduate study |publisher=The University of Edinburgh |accessdate=2020-08-15 |archive-date=2021-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121092319/https://www.ed.ac.uk/divinity/undergraduate |dead-url=no }}</ref> ===
由愛丁堡大學神學系（新學院）所頒發的本科學位共有八個課程，其中有些課程同學可修讀為期四年的榮譽學位（honours degrees），一般學位（general degree）則僅需三年。而當中除了道學學士（Bachelor of Divinity）學位外，其他七個本科課程均會授予畢業同學碩士學位，這包括<ref>{{cite web |author1=The University of Edinburgh |title=Types of programmes |url=https://www.ed.ac.uk/divinity/undergraduate/degree-programmes |website=The University of Edinburgh |publisher=The University of Edinburgh |accessdate=2020-08-15 |archive-date=2020-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029150037/https://www.ed.ac.uk/divinity/undergraduate/degree-programmes |dead-url=no }}</ref>：
* 道學碩士（Master of Divinity）
* 道學與經典文學碩士（MA Divinity and Classics）
* 哲學與神學文學碩士（MA Philosophy and Theology）
* 宗教研究文學碩士（MA Religious Studies）
* 宗教研究與英語文學文學碩士（MA Religious Studies & English Literature）
* 宗教研究與蘇格蘭文學文學碩士（MA Religious Studies & Scottish Literature）
* 神學文學碩士（MA Theology）

=== 研究生/學士後教育 ===
至於愛丁堡大學神學系（新學院）的研究所（graduate school），則分為「修課課程」（taught programmes）與「研究課程」（research programmes)兩大類。<ref>{{cite web |author1=The University of Edinburgh |title=Graduate School |url=https://www.ed.ac.uk/divinity/graduate-school |website=The University of Edinburgh |publisher=The University of Edinburgh |accessdate=2020-08-15 |archive-date=2019-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191125201019/https://www.ed.ac.uk/divinity/graduate-school |dead-url=no }}</ref>
==== 修課課程<ref>{{cite web |author1=The University of Edinburgh |title=Taught programmes |url=https://www.ed.ac.uk/divinity/graduate-school/taught-programmes |website=The University of Edinburgh |publisher=The University of Edinburgh |accessdate=2020-08-15 |archive-date=2018-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180217202937/https://www.ed.ac.uk/divinity/graduate-school/taught-programmes |dead-url=no }}</ref> ====
某些「修課課程」（taught programmes）的同學可以挑選以「神學碩士」（Master of Theology）或「理科碩士」（Master of Science）的學位頭銜修讀，主要攻讀的領域有：
* 聖經研究（Biblical Studies）
* 伊斯蘭與基督徒-穆斯林關係（Islam and Christian-Muslim relations）
* 宗教研究（Religious Studies）
* 科學與宗教（Science and Religion）
* 神學的歷史（Theology in History）
* 世界基督教（World Christianity）

除一般「神學碩士」、「理科碩士」學位外，神學系還提供給其他非神學本科學位畢業的人士修讀「神學與宗教研究學士後文憑」（Graduate Diploma in Theology & Religious Studies）課程<ref>{{cite web |author1=The University of Edinburgh |title=Graduate Diploma in Theology & Religious Studies |url=https://www.ed.ac.uk/divinity/graduate-school/taught-programmes/graduate-diploma |website=The University of Edinburgh |publisher=The University of Edinburgh |accessdate=2020-08-15 |archive-date=2021-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211218134413/https://www.ed.ac.uk/divinity/graduate-school/taught-programmes/graduate-diploma |dead-url=no }}</ref>；神學系也有與大學裡的哲學系合辦的「哲學、科學與宗教線上理科碩士」（Online MSc Philosophy, Science and Religion）學位<ref>{{cite web |author1=The University of Edinburgh |title=Online MSc Philosophy, Science and Religion |url=https://www.ed.ac.uk/divinity/graduate-school/taught-programmes/online-msc-philosophy-science-and-religion |website=The University of Edinburgh |publisher=The University of Edinburgh |accessdate=2020-08-15 |archive-date=2021-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303033504/https://www.ed.ac.uk/divinity/graduate-school/taught-programmes/online-msc-philosophy-science-and-religion |dead-url=no }}</ref>；自2021年六月開始，神學系則會開始「教牧博士」（Doctor of Ministry）課程<ref>{{cite web |author1=The University of Edinburgh |title=Ministry |url=https://www.ed.ac.uk/divinity/graduate-school/taught-programmes/doctor-of-ministry |website=The University of Edinburgh |publisher=The University of Edinburgh |accessdate=2020-08-15 |archive-date=2021-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210305165807/https://www.ed.ac.uk/divinity/graduate-school/taught-programmes/doctor-of-ministry |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==== 研究課程 ====
神學系所提供的「研究課程」則分為四大類<ref>{{cite web |author1=The University of Edinburgh |title=Types of programmes |url=https://www.ed.ac.uk/divinity/graduate-school/research-programmes/types-of-programmes |website=The University of Edinburgh |publisher=The University of Edinburgh |accessdate=2020-08-15 |archive-date=2021-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303041823/https://www.ed.ac.uk/divinity/graduate-school/research-programmes/types-of-programmes |dead-url=no }}</ref>：
