* 哲學碩士（Master of Philosophy），【為期兩年】

「研究課程」與以上所述的「修課課程」的專攻領域略微不同，其中包含<ref>{{cite web |author1=The University of Edinburgh |title=Research study areas |url=https://www.ed.ac.uk/divinity/studying/graduate-school/research-programmes/study-areas |website=The University of Edinburgh |publisher=The University of Edinburgh |accessdate=2020-08-15 |archive-date=2020-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200815193701/https://www.ed.ac.uk/divinity/studying/graduate-school/research-programmes/study-areas |dead-url=no }}</ref>：
